{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-010","title":"Sentence 10","sectionId":"sentences-001","sectionTitle":"Sentence 01-10","pageStart":77,"pageEnd":82,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":40,"duplicateEntryCount":1,"pages":[{"number":77,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 10"},{"type":"text","text":"Fungi are important in the process of decay, which returns"},{"type":"text","text":"ingredients to the soil, enhances soil fertility, and decomposes animal"},{"type":"text","text":"debris."},{"type":"text","text":"真菌在腐化过程中十分重要，腐化过程将各种成分回馈于土"},{"type":"text","text":"壤，提高其肥力，并分解动物残骸。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句的主干是Fungi are important。which引导的定语从句用来修饰"},{"type":"text","text":"the process of decay。该定语从句中有三个并列的谓语：returns、"},{"type":"text","text":"enhances和decomposes。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"fungus /ˈfʌŋɡəs/ n. [pl. fungi]真菌，菌类植物","headword":"fungus"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 fungal a. 真菌的"},{"type":"text","text":"fungicide n. 杀真菌剂"},{"type":"note","text":"参考 bacteria n. [复]细菌"},{"type":"entry","text":"decay /dɪˈkeɪ/ v. （使）腐烂，腐朽","headword":"decay"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 骗（decoy）人变坏（decay）"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 rot v. 腐烂"},{"type":"entry","text":"ingredient /ɪnˈɡriːdiənt/ n. 成分；原料；要素","headword":"ingredient"}]},{"number":78,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"记忆 in（里，内）+gred（=grad进入）+ient→构成物体的内部物"},{"type":"text","text":"质→成分"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 element n. 成分"},{"type":"entry","text":"soil /sɔɪl/ n. 土地，土壤","headword":"soil"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 破坏（spoil）土地（soil），损人不利己"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 soil erosion 土壤侵蚀"},{"type":"entry","text":"enhance /ɪnˈhæns/ vt. 提高；增强","headword":"enhance"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 en（使…）＋hance（高）→提高；增强"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 enhance one’s reputation 提高声誉"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 enhancement n. 增加"},{"type":"text","text":"enhanced a. 增强的；提高的"},{"type":"entry","text":"fertility /fərˈtɪləti/ n. 肥沃，多产","headword":"fertility"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 fertility rate 生育率"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 fertile a. 肥沃的，富饶的"},{"type":"entry","text":"decompose /ˌdiːkəmˈpoʊz/ v. （使）分解；","headword":"decompose"},{"type":"text","text":"（使）腐烂"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 de（分离）+compose（组成）→把组合在一起的东西分开"},{"type":"text","text":"→（使）分解"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 disintegrate vi. 分解"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 decomposition n. 分解；腐烂"},{"type":"entry","text":"debris /dəˈbriː/ n. 废墟，残骸","headword":"debris"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 remains n. 废墟，残骸"},{"type":"text","text":"fragment n. 碎片"},{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"},{"type":"text","text":"与“真菌”相关的词："}]},{"number":79,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"antibiotics /ˌæntibaɪˈɑːtɪk/ n. 抗生素","headword":"antibiotics"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 potent antibiotics 强效抗生素"},{"type":"entry","text":"assimilation /əˌsɪməˈleɪʃn/ n. 同化作用","headword":"assimilation"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 as+simil（相同）+ation→使相同→同化"},{"type":"entry","text":"bamboo-sun /ˌbæmˈbuːsʌn/ n. 竹荪","headword":"bamboo-sun"},{"type":"entry","text":"dissimilation /ˌdɪsɪmɪˈleɪʃən/ n. 异化作用","headword":"dissimilation"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 cultural dissimilation 文化异化"},{"type":"entry","text":"enzyme /ˈenzaɪm/ n. 酶","headword":"enzyme"}]},{"number":80,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"搭配 enzyme activity酶活力"},{"type":"entry","text":"fermentation /ˌfɜːrmenˈteɪʃn/ n. 发酵","headword":"fermentation"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 ferment v. （使）发酵"},{"type":"text","text":"fermenter n. 发酵物"},{"type":"entry","text":"heterotroph /ˈhetərətrɑːf/ n. 异养生物","headword":"heterotroph"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 heterotrophic a. 非自养的"},{"type":"text","text":"jelly ear fungus 木耳"},{"type":"entry","text":"lichen /ˈlaɪkən/ n. 地衣，青苔","headword":"lichen"},{"type":"entry","text":"mold /moʊld/ n. 霉菌","headword":"mold"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 blue mold青霉"},{"type":"entry","text":"mushroom /ˈmʌʃrʊm/ n. 蘑菇","headword":"mushroom"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 mushroom cloud 蘑菇云"},{"type":"entry","text":"